data.description: Step into contemporary luxury with this pristine 4-bedroom, 2-and-a-half-bathroom home that effortlessly combines style and functionality. Built in 2021, this residence embodies the best of modern living. Experience the epitome of spaciousness with the open concept floor plan, seamlessly blending the kitchen, living, and dining areas. This design creates a welcoming atmosphere, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality family time. From the chic design elements to the practical layout, every detail of this home exudes charm and functionality. The thoughtfully crafted spaces showcase a commitment to quality and comfort. This home offers the luxury of separate living and dining rooms, providing versatility in how you use your living space. Whether hosting formal dinners or enjoying casual gatherings, these distinct areas cater to your lifestyle. Retreat to the expansive owner's suite, a haven of comfort and relaxation. Discover the luxury of a sitting area, creating a private retreat within your own home. This oversized bedroom offers a tranquil escape from the everyday hustle. Indulge in the ensuite bathroom's spa-like atmosphere featuring double vanities, a separate shower, & soaking tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day. The well-appointed design provides a serene and luxurious space to pamper yourself. The additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed, providing ample space for family members or guests. Each room offers comfort and flexibility, making them ideal for various needs. Unwind and entertain on the covered patio, an extension of your living space that invites relaxation and al fresco dining. The perfect spot to enjoy the beautiful weather and create lasting memories. Also, enjoy the convenience of a two-car garage, providing secure parking and additional storage space. Easily access your vehicles and keep belongings organized in this practical and well-designed feature. This 2-story residence is a testament to modern design and convenience, offering a lifestyle tailored to the needs of today's homeowners. Don't miss the opportunity to call this meticulously maintained property your new home. Schedule a showing and experience the unparalleled charm for yourself!
